02:24 --> 02:33
Even at night, when the
stars come out, that's their sign
----
Incluso de noche, cuando salen las
estrellas esa es la señal de ellos

27
02:34 --> 02:39
They always know the area where they are going to eat
----
Siempre saben la zona donde van a comer

28
02:41 --> 02:47
