04:02 --> 04:06
The wind is very good for fishing
----
El viento es muy bueno para pescar

43
04:08 --> 04:15
The wind comes from the southwest and pushes the boats there
----
El viento viene del suroeste y empuja las lanchas hacia allá

44
04:16 --> 04:21
Little by little into the sea
----
Poco a poco a mar adentro

